WITH InquiryData AS (
    SELECT 
        ds2.ServiceId,
        ds2.ProgressId,
        COUNT(ds2.Id) AS value
    FROM InquiryDetail ds2
    JOIN Inquiry ds1 ON ds2.InquiryId = ds1.Id
    WHERE ds1.TypeId = 1 
        AND ds2.UserReceiverId = '{TokenUserId}' 
        AND ds2.InsertedDate >= '{FromDate}' 
        AND ds2.InsertedDate < '{ToDate}'
    GROUP BY ds2.ServiceId, ds2.ProgressId
),
ServiceMapping AS (
    SELECT 1 AS ServiceId, 'Air Export' AS name UNION ALL
    SELECT 2, 'Air Import' UNION ALL
    SELECT 3, 'Sea Export FCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 4, 'Sea Import FCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 5, 'Sea Export LCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 6, 'Sea Import LCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 9, 'Logistics' UNION ALL
    SELECT 15, 'FCL TRUCKING' UNION ALL
    SELECT 10, 'FTL TRUCKING' UNION ALL
    SELECT 12, 'LTL TRUCKING' UNION ALL
    SELECT 14, 'Other Logistics'
),
ProgressTypes AS (
    SELECT 1 AS ProgressId UNION ALL
    SELECT 2 UNION ALL
    SELECT 3 UNION ALL
    SELECT 4 UNION ALL
    SELECT 5
)
SELECT 
    s.name,
    p.ProgressId,
    COALESCE(d.value, 0) AS value
FROM ServiceMapping s
CROSS JOIN ProgressTypes p
LEFT JOIN InquiryData d ON s.ServiceId = d.ServiceId AND p.ProgressId = d.ProgressId
ORDER BY s.name, p.ProgressId;

SELECT 'Pending' AS name, COUNT(*) AS value 
FROM ShipmentTask  ds2
WHERE ds2.IsFinish = 0 AND ds2.InsertedBy = '{TokenUserId}'  and ds2.JobDate >= '{FromDate}' and ds2.JobDate < '{ToDate}'
UNION ALL
SELECT 'Completed' AS name, COUNT(*) AS value 
FROM ShipmentTask ds2
WHERE ds2.IsFinish = 1 AND ds2.InsertedBy = '{TokenUserId}'  and ds2.JobDate >= '{FromDate}' and ds2.JobDate < '{ToDate}'
UNION ALL
SELECT 'Overdue' AS name, COUNT(*) AS value 
FROM ShipmentTask ds2 
WHERE ((ds2.FinishDate > ds2.EstimateFinishDate and ds2.EstimateFinishDate is not null) or (ds2.EstimateFinishDate < GetDate() and ds2.FinishDate is null and ds2.EstimateFinishDate is not null)) AND ds2.InsertedBy = '{TokenUserId}'  and ds2.JobDate >= '{FromDate}' and ds2.JobDate < '{ToDate}'

WITH TypeMapping AS (
    SELECT 1 AS TypeId, 'Air Export' AS Name UNION ALL
    SELECT 2, 'Air Import' UNION ALL
    SELECT 3, 'Sea Export FCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 4, 'Sea Import FCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 5, 'Sea Export LCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 6, 'Sea Import LCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 16, 'Sea Import Consol' UNION ALL
    SELECT 17, 'Sea Export Consol' UNION ALL
    SELECT 13, 'Trucking' UNION ALL
    SELECT 9, 'Logistics' UNION ALL
    SELECT 14, 'Other Logistics'
)

SELECT 
    COUNT(ds2.Id) AS value, 
    tm.Name AS name
FROM TypeMapping tm
JOIN Shipment ds2 ON ds2.TypeId = tm.TypeId
    AND ds2.ParentId IS NULL
    AND ds2.InsertedBy = '{TokenUserId}'  
    AND ds2.ShipmentDate >= '{FromDate}' 
    AND ds2.ShipmentDate < '{ToDate}'
GROUP BY tm.TypeId, tm.Name
HAVING COUNT(ds2.Id) > 0;

WITH TypeMapping AS (
    SELECT 1 AS TypeId, 'Air Export' AS Name UNION ALL
    SELECT 2, 'Air Import' UNION ALL
    SELECT 3, 'Sea Export FCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 4, 'Sea Import FCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 5, 'Sea Export LCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 6, 'Sea Import LCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 16, 'Sea Import Consol' UNION ALL
    SELECT 17, 'Sea Export Consol' UNION ALL

    SELECT 9, 'Logistics' UNION ALL
    SELECT 14, 'Other Logistics'
)

SELECT 
    COUNT(ds2.Id) AS value, 
    tm.Name AS name
FROM TypeMapping tm
JOIN Shipment ds2 ON ds2.TypeId = tm.TypeId
    AND ds2.ParentId IS NOT NULL
    AND ds2.InsertedBy = '{TokenUserId}'  
    AND ds2.ShipmentDate >= '{FromDate}' 
    AND ds2.ShipmentDate < '{ToDate}'
GROUP BY tm.TypeId, tm.Name
HAVING COUNT(ds2.Id) > 0;

SELECT 
    all_types.name, 
    COALESCE(subquery.value, 0) AS value
FROM (
    SELECT 
        COUNT(ds2.Id) AS value, 
        CASE 
            WHEN ds2.ServiceId = 1 THEN 'Air Export'
            WHEN ds2.ServiceId = 2 THEN 'Air Import'
            WHEN ds2.ServiceId = 3 THEN 'Sea Export FCL'
            WHEN ds2.ServiceId = 4 THEN 'Sea Import FCL'
            WHEN ds2.ServiceId = 5 THEN 'Sea Export LCL'
            WHEN ds2.ServiceId = 6 THEN 'Sea Import LCL'
            WHEN ds2.ServiceId = 16 THEN 'Sea Import Consol'
            WHEN ds2.ServiceId = 17 THEN 'Sea Export Consol'
            WHEN ds2.ServiceId = 13 THEN 'Trucking'
            WHEN ds2.ServiceId = 9 THEN 'Logistics'
        END AS name
    FROM Booking ds2
    WHERE ds2.TypeId IN (6,7,8,9) 
        AND ds2.ReceiverIds LIKE '%{TokenUserId}%' 
        AND ds2.ShipmentId IS NOT NULL 
        AND ds2.InsertedDate >= '{FromDate}' 
        AND ds2.InsertedDate < '{ToDate}'
    GROUP BY ds2.ServiceId
) AS subquery
RIGHT JOIN (
    SELECT 'Air Export' AS name UNION ALL
    SELECT 'Air Import' UNION ALL
    SELECT 'Sea Export FCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 'Sea Import FCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 'Sea Export LCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 'Sea Import LCL' UNION ALL
    SELECT 'Sea Import Consol' UNION ALL
    SELECT 'Sea Export Consol' UNION ALL
    SELECT 'Trucking' UNION ALL
    SELECT 'Logistics'
) AS all_types ON subquery.name = all_types.name
ORDER BY name asc;

    FROM Shipment ds2

    AND ds2.ShipmentDate >= '{FromDate}' 
    AND ds2.ShipmentDate < '{ToDate}'
